data.description: This is a fantastic recently updated rare end-unit townhome with an attached garage, ready for you to move-in, in the desirable Utah Park neighborhood! From top to bottom, this unit has been renovated. Enjoy open-concept living in the bright and airy main living space perfect for entertaining! The living room has a lot of natural light because there is walk-out access through sliding glass doors onto the private balcony which is the perfect spot to relax and enjoy Colorado's 300 days of sunshine! The dining room flows seamlessly into the kitchen which boasts stainless steel appliances and chic white cabinetry. Down the hallway, discover two also very sunny generously-sized bedrooms, a full bathroom, and ultra-convenient in-unit laundry! Having a side-by-side laundry suite in unit is very hard to find. There is also extra storage space for laundry products, or extra linens. This unit is directly above the oversized attached garage and features additional storage space for all of the extra storage items you may have! This home has been completely updated and features brand new flooring, a new range, a new range hood, a new dishwasher, new lighting, and fresh paint! This location is really in such a great location, walk-able to the hospital, lightrail station, close to shopping, dining, entertainment, and more! Enjoy exploring your new neighborhood with walks to Utah Park and Jewell Wetlands Park. It also has really easy access to the interstate for easy commutes or weekend adventures. You can hop to many areas of town and through the city within minutes. Come see it today, and have a new home for the holiday season!
